imdb.plot outline: In this new series, one couple asks the question, "Would we be together in parallel universes?" Part One explores the lives of 2 assassins who met on the job, dated, but after the break up, how will Alex handle being told to take out her ex, Sam, after she tried to get out of the game. Part Two explores a Romantic Comedy world without internet and how Sam and Alex will make it work after meeting at a bridal shower. Part Three explores a world where the zombie apocalypse has hit. Will Sam and Alex be able to survive the living dead as well as each other?
